{"items":[{"id":"62277","user":{"id":"410179","nickname":"小笛笛","avatar_url":"https://static.codemao.cn/FuAA7vcS9nOxjLFQGi5ReK2dm6gr","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p>666</p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1516173558,"created_at":1516173558,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"61646","user":{"id":"402140","nickname":"清华大学 Dr.潘","avatar_url":"https://static.codemao.cn/FhU5wbKdRGIXqYLv2ubl9MAM55-_","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p>联合概率公式具体是指哪道式子呀</p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1515846613,"created_at":1515846613,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"61622","user":{"id":"133721","nickname":"四九圣尊","avatar_url":"https://static.codemao.cn/FpwY7hm51Irx8lFHBCthzIBrYbJt","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p>那么联合概率公式呢？好像把这些都算出来求平均值不行。不太准，还有发我先假设一个词在健康邮件出现的概率很重要，对结果影响很大</p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1515843409,"created_at":1515843409,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"61584","user":{"id":"402140","nickname":"清华大学 Dr.潘","avatar_url":"https://static.codemao.cn/FhU5wbKdRGIXqYLv2ubl9MAM55-_","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p>这就是上面计算公式的含义，有什么不明白的你直接在下面回复哈</p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1515823080,"created_at":1515823080,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"61583","user":{"id":"402140","nickname":"清华大学 Dr.潘","avatar_url":"https://static.codemao.cn/FhU5wbKdRGIXqYLv2ubl9MAM55-_","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p>要求P(S|W)，就是已知一封邮件包含sex单词，那么该邮件是垃圾邮件的概率，我就要把所有包含sex单词的邮件全部拿出来，再计算其中垃圾邮件的比例，像下图展示的那样</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FtNCOP9rTDdVMXCWcIoZoWhSkMBv\"><br></p>\n<p><br></p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1515822930,"created_at":1515822930,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"61582","user":{"id":"402140","nickname":"清华大学 Dr.潘","avatar_url":"https://static.codemao.cn/FhU5wbKdRGIXqYLv2ubl9MAM55-_","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/Ft1ubR4j3QWvrIvmqpNt3q7Vbpyi\"><br></p>\n<p>这幅图是对所有情况的分解</p>\n<p><br></p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1515822878,"created_at":1515822878,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"61580","user":{"id":"402140","nickname":"清华大学 Dr.潘","avatar_url":"https://static.codemao.cn/FhU5wbKdRGIXqYLv2ubl9MAM55-_","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p>第一道式子里面，P(S ｜ W)指包含了sex这个词的邮件是垃圾邮件的概率，P(W｜S)和P(S)的含义前文已经解释了，把他们乘起来得到的是一封邮件既包含了sex这个词同时又是垃圾邮件的概率，P(W)是一封邮件包含sex这个词的概率</p>\n<p><br></p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1515822495,"created_at":1515822495,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"61576","user":{"id":"402140","nickname":"清华大学 Dr.潘","avatar_url":"https://static.codemao.cn/FhU5wbKdRGIXqYLv2ubl9MAM55-_","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p>图里面的内容应该是这个，我给你一步步解释一下哈</p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1515821209,"created_at":1515821209,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"61575","user":{"id":"402140","nickname":"清华大学 Dr.潘","avatar_url":"https://static.codemao.cn/FhU5wbKdRGIXqYLv2ubl9MAM55-_","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/Foi3iQkE7nGN1eTJnX4bjpjXn4T0\"><br></p>\n<p><br></p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1515821166,"created_at":1515821166,"earliest_comments":[]}