"nickname":"四九圣尊","avatar_url":"https://static.codemao.cn/FpwY7hm51Irx8lFHBCthzIBrYbJt","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p><img src=\"http://img.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/af/kl_thumb.gif\"><br></p>\n<p><br></p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1515756361,"created_at":1515756361,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"60632","user":{"id":"133721","nickname":"四九圣尊","avatar_url":"https://static.codemao.cn/FpwY7hm51Irx8lFHBCthzIBrYbJt","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p>大神们快过来给我补公式了</p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1515213356,"created_at":1515213356,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"60607","user":{"id":"133721","nickname":"四九圣尊","avatar_url":"https://static.codemao.cn/FpwY7hm51Irx8lFHBCthzIBrYbJt","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p><p>import nltk import os from nltk.book import * import numpy from nltk import * from sklearn import * import easygui from nltk.corpus import stopwords english_stopwords = stopwords.words('english') xianyan = 0.5 ku = [] pass133 = os.getcwd() + \"\\\\R\" pass134 = os.getcwd() + \"\\\\H\" a = os.listdir(pass133) aa = os.listdir(pass134) txt_place= \"\" txt_text = \"\" htxt_place = \"\" htxt_text = \"\" print(\"开始学习！\") for i in range(len(a)): ku_fu = [] txt_place = os.getcwd() + \"\\R\" + \"\\\\\" + a[i] print(txt_place) txt_text = open(txt_place).read() txt_text = txt_text.lower() ku_fu = word_tokenize(txt_text) ku.extend(ku_fu) hku = [] for i in range(len(aa)): hku_fu = [] htxt_place =os.getcwd() + \"\\H\" + \"\\\\\" + aa[i] print(htxt_place) htxt_text = open(htxt_place).read() htxt_text = htxt_text.lower() hku_fu = word_tokenize(htxt_text) hku.extend(hku_fu) print(hku) number = [\"second\",\"third\",\"fourth\",\"fifth\",\"sixth\",\"seventh\",\"eighth\",\"ninth\",\"tenth\"] ku_he = ku ciping = [] zuizhong = [] ku = [w for w in ku if w not in english_stopwords and len(w) &gt;= 5 and w.isalpha() and w not in number] hku = [w for w in hku if w not in english_stopwords and len(w) &gt;= 5 and w.isalpha() and w not in number] print(hku) fdist1 = FreqDist(ku) print(fdist1) zuizhong_fu = list(fdist1) print(\"INIT SUCCESS\") for i in zuizhong_fu: zuizhong.append(i) if fdist1[i]/len(a) &gt;= 1: ciping.append(1) elif fdist1[i]/len(a) &lt; 1: ciping.append(float(fdist1[i]/len(a))) pass10 = input(\"词汇矩阵构建完成！点击enter开始测试垃圾邮件！\") txt = easygui.fileopenbox(default='*.txt') text = open(txt).read() text = text.lower() text_fen = word_tokenize(text) text_fen = list(set(text_fen)) wenti = [] gongyou = [] for i in range(len(text_fen)): if text_fen[i] in zuizhong: gongyou.append(text_fen[i]) hwenti = [] for i in range(len(gongyou)): pass90 = hku.count(gongyou[i]) hwenti.append(pass90) for i in range(len(gongyou)): hwenti[i] = hwenti[i]/len(hku)*100 for i in range(len(gongyou)): wula = zuizhong.index(gongyou[i]) print(\"抽取：\" + str(wula)) wenti.append(float(ciping[wula]*100)) zuihouha = []&nbsp;</p>\n<p>就剩最后那个公式了，大佬帮帮我吧！</p></p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1515159550,"created_at":1515159550,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"60590","user":{"id":"133721","nickname":"四九圣尊","avatar_url":"https://static.codemao.cn/FpwY7hm51Irx8lFHBCthzIBrYbJt","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FhX4e4FmfzDDrpWE_y1wZj0UnpU7\"><br></p>\n<p>急，帮我把这张图的内容写给我，用比较通俗的语言</p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1515154566,"created_at":1515154566,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"60563","user":{"id":"219792","nickname":"咚当家族编辑部","avatar_url":"https://static.codemao.cn/FiMx4sfjLjzULIJ_aHZnOg0iNPHB","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">虽然当当不是太会算法</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">但给你参考下吧</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">流程图如下</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/Fjj-HfYzJnfxnRwhj8K-35mXxSPD\"><br></p>\n<p><br></p></p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1515145003,"created_at":1515145003,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"60559","user":{"id":"133721","nickname":"四九圣尊","avatar_url":"https://static.codemao.cn/FpwY7hm51Irx8lFHBCthzIBrYbJt","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/Fiuldn1eHQjbcIJx4iur_vbowfbT\"><br></p>\n<p>我要开始优化我的算法了，博士，这里的图没了我学习不了，麻烦您帮我把图补上，用比较简单易懂的算式谢谢</p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1515141487,"created_at":1515141487,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"60165","user":{"id":"133721","nickname":"四九圣尊","avatar_url":"https://static.codemao.cn/FpwY7hm51Irx8lFHBCthzIBrYbJt","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p><img src=\"http://img.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/5c/huanglianwx_thumb.gif\"><br></p>\n<p><br></p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1514812823,"created_at":1514812823,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"60041","user":{"id":"402140","nickname":"清华大学 Dr.潘","avatar_url":"https://static.codemao.cn/FhU5wbKdRGIXqYLv2ubl9MAM55-_","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p>下面是几个公开的垃圾邮件数据库：</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://c喵ining.org/index.php/spam-assassin-datasets.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">http://c喵ining.org/index.php/spam-assassin-datasets.html</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://c喵ining.org/index.php/ling-spam-datasets.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">http://c喵ining.org/index.php/ling-spam-datasets.html</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://plg.uwaterloo.ca/\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://plg.uwaterloo.ca/</a>~gvcormac/treccorpus/</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://nlp.cs.aueb.gr/software_and_datasets/Enron-Spam/index.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">http://nlp.cs.aueb.gr/software_and_datasets/Enron-Spam/index.html</a></p>\n<p>如果想自己找的话，可以试试在搜索引擎上输入spam classification dataset这样的关键词来找。</p>\n<p><br></p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1514782679,"created_at":1514782679,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"60038","user":{"id":"402140","nickname":"清华大学 Dr.潘","avatar_url":"https://static.codemao.cn/FhU5wbKdRGIXqYLv2ubl9MAM55-_","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p>如果概念已经get了的话可以试试一下叫sklearn的python包，可以通过</p>\n<p>pip install -U scikit-learn</p>\n<p>来安装，里面包含有朴素贝叶斯的实现，下面是例子：</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://scikit-learn.org/stable/modules/naive_bayes.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">http://scikit-learn.org/stable/modules/naive_bayes.html</a></p>\n<p>如果还想看具体的实现，可以看：</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/scikit-learn/scikit-learn/blob/a24c8b46/sklearn/naive_bayes.py#L160\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://github.com/scikit-learn/scikit-learn/blob/a24c8b46/sklearn/naive_bayes.py#L160</a></p>\n<p>还有什么问题我们也可以继续讨论</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1514781587,"created_at":1514781587,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"60028","user":{"id":"133721","nickname":"四九圣尊","avatar_url":"https://static.codemao.cn/FpwY7hm51Irx8lFHBCthzIBrYbJt","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p>哪位好心人能给我一个垃圾邮件语料库，最好英文的。中文也ok</p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1514773332,"created_at":1514773332,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"59976","user":{"id":"347681","nickname":"欠王迷","avatar_url":"https://static.codemao.cn/FlX52zFOO8mNzYEXV98WY7ko5qlB","subject_id":1061,"work_shop_name